---
import BaseLayout from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About — About Berlin Hotels"
  description="Who is behind About Berlin Hotels, how we recommend hotels and districts, and how we stay transparent about affiliate links."
  locale="en"
  alternatePath="/ueber-uns/"
>
  <section class="surface-soft border-b border-ink-100">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 sm:px-6 py-12 sm:py-16">
      <span class="text-xs font-bold text-brand-700 uppercase tracking-widest mb-3 block">About</span>
      <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight text-ink-900 text-balance mb-5">
        Your independent Berlin guide to hotels in every district
      </h1>
      <p class="text-lg text-ink-700 leading-relaxed">
        About Berlin Hotels is an editorially curated travel and hotel guide for Berlin. We bring
        hotels, districts, attractions and itineraries together in one place — so you can find the
        right place to stay faster.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <article class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 sm:px-6 py-12 sm:py-16 space-y-10">
    <section>
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight text-ink-900 mb-3">How we pick hotels</h2>
      <p class="text-ink-700 leading-relaxed">
        Our hotel picks are handpicked and deliberately span every price point and style — from grand
        hotels by the Brandenburg Gate to budget houses with great transit links. We vet every property
        against verifiable, publicly documented facts (location, amenities, history). We don't invent
        details. Live prices and availability come straight from Booking.com via embedded maps, so you
        always see current data.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight text-ink-900 mb-3">What we stand for</h2>
      <ul class="space-y-2.5">
        <li class="flex items-start gap-2.5 text-ink-700"><span class="mt-1 inline-flex h-5 w-5 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-brand-600 text-white text-xs font-bold">✓</span><span><strong>Factual accuracy:</strong> based on public sources, checked regularly.</span></li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-2.5 text-ink-700"><span class="mt-1 inline-flex h-5 w-5 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-brand-600 text-white text-xs font-bold">✓</span><span><strong>Local focus:</strong> recommendations by district and trip type, not anonymous lists.</span></li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-2.5 text-ink-700"><span class="mt-1 inline-flex h-5 w-5 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-brand-600 text-white text-xs font-bold">✓</span><span><strong>Freshness:</strong> prices and availability are live, not stale tables.</span></li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-2.5 text-ink-700"><span class="mt-1 inline-flex h-5 w-5 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-brand-600 text-white text-xs font-bold">✓</span><span><strong>Transparency:</strong> affiliate links are clearly labelled.</span></li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight text-ink-900 mb-3">How we're funded</h2>
      <p class="text-ink-700 leading-relaxed">
        To keep this guide free, we work with affiliate partners such as Booking.com (via Stay22) and
        GetYourGuide. If you book through one of our links we earn a small commission — at
        <strong>no extra cost to you</strong>. These commissions don't influence which properties we
        recommend; our selection stays editorial.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight text-ink-900 mb-3">Contact &amp; feedback</h2>
      <p class="text-ink-700 leading-relaxed">
        Missing a hotel, spotted outdated info, or have a tip? Email us at
        <a href="mailto:info@about-berlin-hotels.de" class="text-brand-700 font-medium hover:underline">info@about-berlin-hotels.de</a>.
        Full provider details are in the
        <a href="/en/imprint/" class="text-brand-700 font-medium hover:underline">imprint</a>.
      </p>
    </section>

    <div class="rounded-2xl border border-ink-100 bg-white p-6 sm:p-8">
      <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-ink-900 mb-4">Jump right in</h2>
      <ul class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-2.5">
        <li><a href="/en/districts/" class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 text-brand-700 font-medium hover:underline"><span class="text-brand-400">→</span>Hotels by district</a></li>
        <li><a href="/en/categories/" class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 text-brand-700 font-medium hover:underline"><span class="text-brand-400">→</span>Hotels by category</a></li>
        <li><a href="/en/attractions/" class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 text-brand-700 font-medium hover:underline"><span class="text-brand-400">→</span>Attractions</a></li>
        <li><a href="/en/itineraries/" class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 text-brand-700 font-medium hover:underline"><span class="text-brand-400">→</span>Itineraries</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
